### Define Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@adminAuth = Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW5wYXNz
@userAuth = Basic dXNlcjp1c2VycGFzcw==

@managerAuth = Basic bWFuYWdlcjptYW5hZ2VycGFzcw==

### Public Endpoint (No Authentication)
GET {{baseUrl}}/public
Accept: application/json

### User Endpoint with USER credentials
GET {{baseUrl}}/user
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{userAuth}}

### User Endpoint with ADMIN credentials
GET {{baseUrl}}/user
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### Admin Endpoint with ADMIN credentials
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### Admin Endpoint with USER credentials (should fail with 403 Forbidden)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{userAuth}}

### Alternative: Direct credentials for USER
GET {{baseUrl}}/user
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{userAuth}}

### Alternative: Direct credentials for ADMIN
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### Alternative: Using curl-style auth for ADMIN
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### Manager Endpoint with MANAGER credentials
GET {{baseUrl}}/manager
Accept: application/json
Authorization: {{managerAuth}}
